1
00:01:07,800 --> 00:01:10,080
All our sorrows.

2
00:01:14,600 --> 00:01:15,400
Ruirang.

3
00:01:17,640 --> 00:01:20,920
This dynasty has long been corrupt.

4
00:01:21,800 --> 00:01:26,680
Only blood can wash away the filth of this land.

5
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:57,130
Little Marquis,

6
00:01:57,600 --> 00:01:58,479
excuse me.

7
00:01:58,720 --> 00:02:00,000
Once everything is settled,

8
00:02:00,000 --> 00:02:01,860
I will surely offer the antidote.

9
00:02:04,440 --> 00:02:05,240
Don't forget.

10
00:02:05,600 --> 00:02:07,480
I am Zhou Tiger Song Qingniang,

11
00:02:08,000 --> 00:02:09,400
an expert in using anesthetics.

12
00:02:09,400 --> 00:02:12,060
Curing this poison is naturally a piece of cake.

13
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:14,810
You are actually unaffected by the Gu poison.

14
00:02:56,160 --> 00:02:57,079
Watch out.

15
00:03:01,160 --> 00:03:02,020
Young Marquis.

16
00:03:03,720 --> 00:03:04,250
Ruilang.

17
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:10,400
If you don't want to hand over those letters,

18
00:03:15,720 --> 00:03:16,960
stay with me tonight.

19
00:03:25,440 --> 00:03:26,320
Qin Mengqi.

20
00:03:29,240 --> 00:03:31,760
When you said stay with you,

21
00:03:33,079 --> 00:03:35,480
did you mean standing here in the cold wind?

22
00:03:36,040 --> 00:03:37,040
What else?

23
00:03:38,320 --> 00:03:39,380
What did you think?

24
00:03:44,480 --> 00:03:45,800
I trust you.

25
00:03:54,440 --> 00:03:56,120
By the way,

26
00:03:57,840 --> 00:04:00,170
that was the first time you called my name.

27
00:04:02,160 --> 00:04:03,400
Do you still remember

28
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:06,640
the first time we met?

29
00:04:08,640 --> 00:04:11,480
You were chasing to kill me.

30
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:14,600
Good thing you showed mercy.

31
00:04:16,399 --> 00:04:17,279
Otherwise,

32
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:20,680
I would have been dead long ago.

33
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:25,960
If I had known,

34
00:04:27,880 --> 00:04:29,760
I should have killed you then.

35
00:04:31,680 --> 00:04:33,680
It would have saved a lot of trouble.

36
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:40,280
You should have

37
00:04:43,240 --> 00:04:45,120
killed me right then.

38
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:59,000
Don't move.

39
00:05:07,280 --> 00:05:09,160
Let me lean on your shoulder.

40
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:30,480
Ruilang.

41
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:32,770
If you can persuade your father

42
00:05:32,840 --> 00:05:34,480
before all this is exposed,

43
00:05:35,440 --> 00:05:36,840
he will still be my uncle,

44
00:05:38,200 --> 00:05:40,930
the State Preceptor trusted most by His Majesty.

45
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:50,120
You know what kind of person my father is.

46
00:05:50,920 --> 00:05:52,450
It's easier said than done.

47
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:58,640
You should take care of yourselves first.

48
00:06:09,280 --> 00:06:09,920
Ruilang.

49
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:11,360
Ruilang.

50
00:06:11,760 --> 00:06:12,800
Don't cry.

51
00:06:14,680 --> 00:06:15,160
This,

52
00:06:17,840 --> 00:06:18,920
this may be

53
00:06:19,840 --> 00:06:21,280
my best destiny.

54
00:06:22,280 --> 00:06:22,920
No.

55
00:06:23,320 --> 00:06:23,880
Don't.

56
00:06:24,200 --> 00:06:24,760
Don't.

57
00:06:32,000 --> 00:06:32,800
Don't cry.

58
00:06:34,600 --> 00:06:35,400
If you cry,

59
00:06:36,880 --> 00:06:38,680
I won't like you anymore.

60
00:06:38,680 --> 00:06:39,640
Don't.

61
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,120
Cousin.

62
00:06:50,440 --> 00:06:51,760
Promise me

63
00:06:53,440 --> 00:06:55,720
you'll take good care of Zhaoxue.

64
00:06:57,080 --> 00:07:01,160
Otherwise, I won't let you off even as a ghost.

65
00:07:02,280 --> 00:07:03,080
Okay.

66
00:07:03,440 --> 00:07:06,520
Don't worry, I will definitely take good care of her.

67
00:07:07,280 --> 00:07:08,080
Ruilang.

68
00:07:12,200 --> 00:07:13,000
No.

69
00:07:15,520 --> 00:07:16,320
I am finally

70
00:07:17,840 --> 00:07:18,640
I am finally

71
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:20,760
going to see my mother.

72
00:07:22,760 --> 00:07:23,360
No.

73
00:07:54,320 --> 00:07:55,960
Don't, Qin Mengqi.

74
00:07:56,200 --> 00:07:57,320
No.

75
00:08:00,440 --> 00:08:01,840
Ruilang.

76
00:08:02,320 --> 00:08:03,160
Ruilang.

77
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:09,600
Qin Mengqi,

78
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:11,720
no.

79
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:15,600
Qin Mengqi.

80
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:35,520
Today, I wish to reflect upon my faults, and I hope you, my ministers, will share this lesson.

81
00:09:12,600 --> 00:09:24,360
Today, I wish to reflect upon my faults, and I hope you, my ministers, will share this lesson.

82
00:09:30,520 --> 00:09:33,680
I didn't expect that after so many years,

83
00:09:34,400 --> 00:09:37,400
there are still so many people who remember my father.

84
00:09:38,360 --> 00:09:41,360
Since His Majesty reversed the verdict for Master Su,

85
00:09:41,640 --> 00:09:44,160
the people who have received kindness from the Su family

86
00:09:44,160 --> 00:09:47,440
have been coming in an endless stream to pay their respects to him.

87
00:09:47,440 --> 00:09:48,240
Father.

88
00:09:49,920 --> 00:09:56,480
I have already cleared the name of our Su family for you.

89
00:09:58,040 --> 00:10:00,400
Good people have been protected.

90
00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:04,160
Bad people have been punished.

91
00:10:05,000 --> 00:10:05,800
Father,

92
00:10:06,840 --> 00:10:08,280
you can rest in peace.

93
00:10:09,840 --> 00:10:14,480
Lord Su, everything you did was worth it.

94
00:10:27,680 --> 00:10:28,480
Yan'er.

95
00:10:32,040 --> 00:10:33,640
I miss you so much.

96
00:10:37,160 --> 00:10:39,620
It's my fault for not taking good care of you.

97
00:10:40,280 --> 00:10:44,280
How are you doing over there now?

98
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:49,520
I really want

99
00:10:51,040 --> 00:10:52,970
to reunite with father and mother.

100
00:10:53,600 --> 00:10:54,480
I really miss

101
00:10:56,800 --> 00:10:58,840
our carefree days in the past.

102
00:11:04,520 --> 00:11:05,320
Ruilang.

103
00:11:07,440 --> 00:11:08,480
How are you doing?

104
00:11:09,600 --> 00:11:10,200
I miss you.

105
00:11:12,360 --> 00:11:14,840
Have you met our aunt?

106
00:11:28,400 --> 00:11:29,480
Qin Mengqi.

107
00:11:30,920 --> 00:11:35,320
I didn't expect you to like hearing me call your name.

108
00:11:36,920 --> 00:11:40,280
If I had known, I would have called it more often.

109
00:11:41,040 --> 00:11:43,400
I built a cenotaph for you here.

110
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:45,800
Hope you don't mind.

111
00:11:49,120 --> 00:11:50,200
Now,

112
00:11:52,680 --> 00:11:55,400
you can finally see your mother.

113
00:12:10,320 --> 00:12:11,240
Qin Mengqi.

114
00:12:14,280 --> 00:12:15,610
What you have done for me

115
00:12:16,480 --> 00:12:18,600
and my Su family,

116
00:12:20,440 --> 00:12:24,080
I, Su Zhaoxue, will never forget.

117
00:12:27,360 --> 00:12:28,520
It's just a pity

118
00:12:30,360 --> 00:12:33,320
that I can't be by your side in this life.

119
00:12:36,360 --> 00:12:38,760
I only hope we are destined in the next life.

120
00:12:44,840 --> 00:12:47,120
I will surely repay your deep affection.

121
00:13:04,080 --> 00:13:04,880
Ruilang,

122
00:13:05,840 --> 00:13:07,800
I miss you.

123
00:13:10,080 --> 00:13:13,360
Let's be brothers again in the next life.

124
00:13:15,000 --> 00:13:16,880
I will definitely protect you.

125
00:13:24,280 --> 00:13:25,120
Zhaoxue.

126
00:13:26,120 --> 00:13:27,080
Tell me.

127
00:13:28,480 --> 00:13:29,920
If there is a next life,

128
00:13:31,640 --> 00:13:33,840
would you still want to meet me?

129
00:13:40,720 --> 00:13:41,920
What do you think?

130
00:13:43,680 --> 00:13:46,520
What are your plans now?

131
00:13:47,560 --> 00:13:50,000
I want to go with Jian Da

132
00:13:50,560 --> 00:13:53,000
and Sister Song back to our hometown,

133
00:13:53,560 --> 00:13:56,360
and maybe start a small business.

134
00:13:57,080 --> 00:13:58,200
I'll go with you.

135
00:13:58,480 --> 00:13:59,840
How can you go?

136
00:14:00,320 --> 00:14:02,480
You are the Imperial Censor.

137
00:14:02,600 --> 00:14:04,040
You just solved a major case.

138
00:14:04,040 --> 00:14:05,840
The Emperor highly values you now.

139
00:14:05,840 --> 00:14:07,100
How could he let you go?

140
00:14:10,520 --> 00:14:13,280
I have already asked the Emperor for a leave of absence.

141
00:14:13,280 --> 00:14:16,810
I initially entered politics because of my mother's guidance.

142
00:14:18,000 --> 00:14:19,730
Now that the truth is revealed,

143
00:14:20,320 --> 00:14:22,450
I want to go home to console her spirit.

144
00:14:25,440 --> 00:14:25,970
Besides,

145
00:14:27,040 --> 00:14:29,520
from now on, you must continue to follow me to secure the nation

146
00:14:29,520 --> 00:14:30,650
and save the people.

147
00:14:31,320 --> 00:14:32,320
You can't escape.

148
00:14:32,520 --> 00:14:35,160
If we can stay together tomorrow,

149
00:14:36,080 --> 00:14:37,360
it is for love,

150
00:14:37,760 --> 00:14:41,360
to fulfill our burning hearts.

151
00:14:42,560 --> 00:14:43,360
Don't mention

152
00:14:43,360 --> 00:14:46,160
vows of eternal love.
